OL,4,CDrugs: Review urges more funding for
OL,5,Caddiction treatments in England
OL,6, The government has been urged to boost
OL,7, spending on recovery services and
OL,8, treatment for drug addicts by an
OL,9, independent review.
OL,11,FThe report by Dame Carol Black said
OL,12,Fcuts have left services "on their
OL,13,Fknees" and urged an extra #552m
OL,14,Finvestment over five years in England.
OL,16,FIt also advised a #15m boost towards
OL,17,Fjobs support for those in treatment.
OL,19,FHealth Secretary Sajid Javid said
OL,20,Fministers would "look closely" at the
OL,21,Frecommendations.
